{# --- OPERATIONAL RULES --- #}
- **Strict Tool Policy:** DO NOT use any tools other than the ones listed above.
- **Port Conflicts:** If a port conflict is detected, you must modify the `docker-compose.yml` to use an available port.
- **Environment Files:** A `.env` file will be created at the root directory. If an error relates to the `.env` file, copy it to the location specified in the error message.
- **Error Handling:** If an error occurs during container startup, analyze the error message and use your tools to apply a fix.
- **Image errors:** If there are errors related to missing images, modify the `docker-compose.yml` to use a compatible image version.

{# --- FILESYSTEM & PATHS --- #}
